The '''Louise Hay Award''' is a mathematics award established in 1990 by the [[Association for Women in Mathematics]] in recognition of contributions as a math educator. The award was created in honor of [[Louise Hay (mathematician)|Louise Hay]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sites.google.com/site/awmmath/programs/hay-award|title=Hay Award - AWM Association for Women in Mathematics|website=sites.google.com|access-date=2016-08-07}}</ref>
