uary 2007|website=www.brynmawr.edu|access-date=2016-08-07|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020071034/http://www.brynmawr.edu/sandt/2007_october/briefs.shtml|archivedate=2013-10-20|df=}}</ref> |- |2006 |[[Patricia Clark Kenschaft]]<ref>{{Cite journal|last=|first=|date=May 2006|title=AWM Awards Presented in San Antonio|url=http://www.ams.org/notices/200605/comm-awm.pdf|journal=Notices of the AMS|volume=|issue=|doi=|pmid=|access-date=2016-08-07|via=}}</ref> |- |2005 |[[Susanna S. Epp|Susanna Epp]]<ref>{{Cite journal|last=|first=|date=May 2005|title=AWM Prizes Presented in Atlanta|url=http://www.ams.org/notices/200505/comm-awm.pdf|journal=Notices of the AMS|volume=52|issue=5|doi=|pmid=|access-date=2016-08-07|via=}}</ref> |- |2004 |[[Bozenna Pasik-Duncan]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.math.ku.edu/ksacg/bio.html|title=Bozenna Pasik-Duncan - Biography|website=www.math.ku.edu|access-date=2016-08-07}}</ref> |- |2003 |[[Katherine Puckett Layton]] |- |2002 |[[Annie Selden]] |- |2001 |[[Patricia D. Shure]] |- |2000 |[[Joan Ferrini-Mundy]] |- |1999 |[[Martha K. Smith]] |- |1998 |[[Deborah Hughes Hallett]] |- |1997 |[[Marilyn Burns (Mathematician)|Marilyn Burns]] |- |1996 |[[Glenda Lappan]] and [[Judith Roitman]] |- |1995 |[[Etta Zuber Falconer|Etta Falconer]] |- |1994 |[[Kaye A. de Ruiz]] |- |1993 |[[Naomi Fisher]] |- |1992 |[[Olga Beaver]] |- |1991 |[[Shirley Frye]] |}
